search_results.title: Session Victim · Biography
search_results.snippet: Session Victim are one of Germanys most prolific and accomplished house music production duos today. They are deeply embedded in vinyl culture.

search_results.title: Session Victim · Artist Profile
search_results.snippet: Session Victim demonstrate a charming disregard for the boundaries of house music, and unleash an unparalleled energy in their intense live shows.
